        Triggerhappy flies off, then turns around, and goes lower then
transforms to robot mode.  He pulls out his compressed air cannon(Blowpipe)
and fires it up into the sky for no particular reason.

         "I am Decepticon gunner, Triggerhappy!  I demand to know who you
are!!!" He yells.
